text: Jahanara Alam (born: 1 April 1993) is a Bangladeshi cricketer who plays for the Bangladesh national women's cricket team. She is a right-arm medium fast bowler and right-handed batswoman. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Cricketers from Khulna Division
